163
00:15:11,094 --> 00:15:12,374
Perché non è vero!

164
00:15:12,433 --> 00:15:12,894
Calma, Leo.

165
00:15:14,095 --> 00:15:14,995
Ti fai anche male alla mamma.

166
00:15:15,115 --> 00:15:15,875
Vai, fammi vedere.

167
00:15:15,894 --> 00:15:16,475
Lasciami stare.

168
00:15:16,495 --> 00:15:18,115
Fammi vedere, Leo.

169
00:15:18,135 --> 00:15:29,500
Leo!

170
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:30,140
