00:33:26,719 --> 00:33:32,323
Lo spero davvero.

481
00:33:32,383 --> 00:33:33,202
Allora posso restare?

482
00:33:36,305 --> 00:33:36,704
Sì, puoi.

483
00:33:36,765 --> 00:33:36,884
Grazie.

484
00:33:43,663 --> 00:33:53,707
